132	                <span class="text-xs text-stone">Baby is the size of</span>
133	                <span class="bg-blush/20 text-lavender px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold">Papaya</span>
134	              </div>
135	            </div>
136	          </div>
137	        </div>
138	
